                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-340-off1837 t18300415-340-cd1838"></join>, 1 tin box, value 1d.; 2 sovereigns, and 9s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-340-victim2815" type="victimName">
                           James 
